main event: Multiple witnesses in Maysville, Kentucky reported seeing bright, luminescent objects in the sky on February 9, 1963.
interesting points: Witnesses described the objects as bright lights that changed color from white to red,The sightings included details of the object moving at high speeds and making erratic maneuvers,One witness claimed to have observed the object for approximately 10 minutes,The case was investigated by Dr. J. Allen Hynek, a noted UFO researcher,Photographs were taken by a witness, although the report states that the images do not contain clear evidence of the objects.
witness description: A 34-year-old housewife observed a bright orange light.
